<%# About %>
<div class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container about-section py-5">
    <div class="row d-flex g-5 justify-content-between align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
        <div class="about-img shadow-effect" data-aos="fade-up" style="background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/1459331/pexels-photo-1459331.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1');">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 bg-white" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="about-content p-3">
          <h4>About <span class="fw-bold display-6">Guavaaa</span></h4>
          <h6 class="text-dark display-7">Transitioning from being a construction worker to a fruit and vegetable farmer is tougher
          than changing careers to coding. After all, it requires a combination of physical and mental
          prowess. <strong>However, Mr. Pan, driven by an undying spirit, made the courageous decision to
          convert his rice fields into a sprawling fruit and vegetable garden. He began by cultivating
          sour kumquats, and then delved into the realms of guava and corn cultivation.</strong>
          It's not mere showmanship; numerous reviews have attested to Mr. Pan's exceptional guavas,
          and his corn harvests never fail to cause a frenzy. If you want to learn more, read on!</h6>
        </div>
        <img class="avatar-large" alt="avatar-large" src="https://kitt.lewagon.com/placeholder/users/arthur-littm" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%# About %>

